Description:
Character set conversion of strings made easy, uses iconv, with out-of-memory
checking.

Files:
lib/xstriconv.h
lib/xstriconv.c

Depends-on:
striconv
xalloc

configure.ac:

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += xstriconv.h xstriconv.c

Include:
"xstriconv.h"

Link:
$(LTLIBICONV) when linking with libtool, $(LIBICONV) otherwise

License:
GPL

Maintainer:
Simon Josefsson
